  "title": "DIRECTOR",
  "description": "<p>We need Company Director with below requirements;</p><ul><li>Develop and lead the overall marketing strategy aligned with company goals and market dynamics.</li><li>Set departmental objectives, KPIs, and long-term vision for brand growth and market penetration.</li><li>Act as the strategic marketing advisor to the executive leadership team.</li><li>Define and elevate brand identity, tone, and positioning across all markets.</li><li>Ensure consistent brand messaging across all channels and regions.</li><li>Oversee the planning, execution, and performance of integrated marketing campaigns across digital, print, media, and events.</li><li>Direct market research initiatives to understand customer needs, market trends, and competitive positioning.</li><li>Use insights and data analytics to inform strategy, product development, and go-to-market plans.</li><li>Build, lead, and mentor a high-performing marketing team.</li><li>Set performance objectives and guide career development of team members.</li><li>Develop and manage the marketing department budget.</li><li>Allocate resources effectively to maximize ROI on campaigns and initiatives.</li><li>Evaluate agency partnerships and ensure cost-effective outsourcing.</li><li>Manage high-level communications, PR strategies, and crisis communication plans.</li><li>Serve as the company’s brand ambassador at public events, media appearances, and industry forums.</li></ul><p>Qualifications</p><ul><li>10+ years of experience in a sales or a similar client-facing role.</li><li>Strong understanding of sales processes and customer relationship management (CRM) software.</li><li>Excellent communication, negotiation, and presentation skills.</li><li>Ability to work independently and as part of a team in a fast-paced environment.</li><li>Willingness to travel.</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Adeline Tan</p><p>EA Licence Number: 23C1668</p><p>Registration Number: R23115708</p><p>Ezline Pte Ltd</p>",
